      %p
        Maybe it’s not quite what you were expecting, this autumn winter, but once you take a moment and think about it, you might see that it makes absolute sense. in a time of work wear crisis, this suit could solve all our problems in one go. Are you starting to see where I am coming from now?

      %p
        Remember it’s not complicated, it’s uncomplicated. Life just got easier for you. It’s almost effortless and it has that effortless so chic that we have all admired in someone at some point. 

      %p
        If you have every wanted to acheive that casual smart European look or wondered how to get it, well now is your chance, so grab it. 
      
      %p
        When I put on a baggy suit, I can seriously see myself sat outside a Parisian café having lunch before I saunter back to the office two hours later, still knowing that I could go straight out to dinner in the evening in that very same suit knowing that the fashion police would not come to cart me away mid aperitif. So get your style on and get your suit.

      %p
        Ciao Ciao ladies!!!


